    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for taking a look. I have to be honest\u2014it\u2019s going to be a bit emotional seeing this beauty drive away. I\u2019ve absolutely doted on this car, keeping it tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washing it every single weekend. It\u2019s in truly stunning shape, looking and smelling just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. You might find a microscopic speck here or there if you really go hunting, but she's as close to perfect as they come. It drives like an absolute dream, and I\u2019d love to find someone who will cherish it as much as I have. Come on by, let's have a chat and I'll show you why this is the one!",
