    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a masterfully sorted E46 M3 in collector-grade condition. This S54 powerplant has been meticulously maintained with a comprehensive VANOS overhaul using Beisan viton seals and a cryo-treated oil pump disk for absolute timing reliability. The chassis rigidity is unsurpassed, featuring a proactive subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings to eliminate deflection during high-load cornering. Throttle mapping is crisp, benefiting from a recent valve adjustment and a bespoke induction setup that optimizes volumetric efficiency. The Getrag 6-speed transmission engages with surgical precision, sending power through a limited-slip differential that remains tight and responsive. Every fluid circuit has been flushed with high-temp synthetics. This is a turn-key, zero-compromise machine for the purist who demands mechanical perfection and tactile feedback.",
      "price": 48500.0,
